Docker workflow
===========================
humen->Client->SERVER-->
			DO I HAVE THAT image iN LR
			YES -Go ahead
			NO - Download from registry.

Container Workflow
=====================================================
create->start->stop->restart->pause->unpause->kill->remove


RUN
==========================
pull->create->start->BECOME

RUN -d
==========================
pull->create->start->BECOME

